Ignatius laughed.

"Pefection! Couldn' have been better. Those tears were a real touch. 
Let's just hope he falls for it.

Meanwhile, something appeared on Prebon's screen.

"Bot...there's a bot closing in on us. He's from a different base, 
but they probably only dit it to make us think they aren't following 
us. Hammer! Take care of it!"

"Yes sir!"

Hammer turned on his Jet Pack and headed for K9's position.

(OOC: Just say somethin about seeing Hammer arrive in the distance 
and than I'll kill. I need you to say it cause you can't go and
